\c 5
\nb
\v 1 Usuphelile umsebenzi wonke uSolomoni ayewenzela indlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*, wangenisa izinto ezingcwelisiweyo zikaDavida uyise, lesiliva legolide lazo zonke izitsha wazibeka esiphaleni senotho sendlu kaNkulunkulu.
\s Ukungeniswa komtshokotsho wesivumelwano ethempelini
\p
\v 2 Ngalesosikhathi uSolomoni wabuthanisa eJerusalema abadala bakoIsrayeli, lazo zonke inhloko zezizwe, izinduna zaboyise babantwana bakoIsrayeli, ukuthi benyuse umtshokotsho wesivumelwano seN\nd kosi\nd* usuke emzini kaDavida oyiZiyoni.
\v 3 Wonke amadoda akoIsrayeli asebuthana enkosini emkhosini owenyanga yesikhombisa\x + 1 Kho. 8.1-9.\x*.
\v 4 Labo bonke abadala bakoIsrayeli beza, amaLevi asewuthwala umtshokotsho\x + 5.7. 1 Kho. 8.3.\x*,
\v 5 awuletha umtshokotsho lethente lenhlangano lazo zonke izitsha ezingcwele ezazisethenteni; abapristi lamaLevi basebekwenyusa\x + 23.18. 1 Kho. 8.4. Dute. 17.18.\x*.
\v 6 Inkosi uSolomoni lenhlangano yonke yakoIsrayeli eyayibuthene phambi komtshokotsho basebenikela imihlatshelo yezimvu lezinkabi ezingelakubhalwa lezingelakubalwa ngobunengi.
\v 7 Abapristi basebewungenisa umtshokotsho wesivumelwano seN\nd kosi\nd* endaweni yawo, endaweni yelizwi yendlu, kungcwele yezingcwele, kwaze kwaba ngaphansi kwempiko \w zamakherubhi\w**.
\v 8 Ngoba \w amakherubhi\w** elulela impiko \add zawo\add* phezu kwendawo yomtshokotsho; amakherubhi awembesa umtshokotsho lemijabo yawo ngaphezulu.
\v 9 Basebeselula imijabo, izihloko zemijabo zaze zabonakala emtshokotshweni phambi kwendawo yelizwi\x + 1 Kho. 8.8.\x*, kodwa zingabonakali ngaphandle; ukhona lapho-ke kuze kube lamuhla.
\v 10 Kwakungelalutho emtshokotshweni, ngaphandle kwezibhebhe ezimbili uMozisi azifaka \add khona\add* eHorebe lapho iN\nd kosi\nd* eyenza khona \add isivumelwano\add* labantwana bakoIsrayeli ekuphumeni kwabo eGibhithe.
\p
\v 11 Kwasekusithi abapristi bephuma endaweni engcwele, ngoba bonke abapristi abatholakalayo babezihlambulule bengagcinanga izigaba,
\v 12 lamaLevi \add ang\add*abahlabeleli babo bonke - akoAsafi, akoHemani, akoJeduthuni, lakumadodana abo lakubafowabo - begqoke amalembu acolekileyo amhlophe, belezinsimbi ezincencethayo lezigubhu zezintambo lamachacho, bema ngempumalanga kwelathi; njalo kanye labo kulabapristi abalikhulu lamatshumi amabili bekhalisa izimpondo.
\v 13 Kwasekusithi bekhalisa izimpondo behlabelela kanyekanye ukuzwakalisa umsindo owodwa, ukudumisa lokubonga iN\nd kosi\nd*, lalapho bephakamisa ilizwi ngezimpondo langezinsimbi ezincencethayo lezinto zokuhlabelela, lalapho bedumisa iN\nd kosi\nd* ukuthi ilungile lokuthi umusa wayo \add umi\add* kuze kube phakade, indlu yagcwaliswa liyezi, indlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*,
\v 14 abapristi kabaze baba lakho ukuma ukukhonza ngenxa yeyezi, ngoba inkazimulo yeN\nd kosi\nd* yagcwalisa indlu kaNkulunkulu.
